                                </a>
                                <a class="dropdown-item d-flex py-3 border-bottom" href="#">
                                    <div class="me-3 notification-icon bg-warning d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
                                        <i class="fas fa-star text-white"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="small text-muted">3 giờ trước</div>
                                        <span class="fw-bold">Đánh giá mới 5 sao từ Nguyễn Thị Thanh</span>
                                    </div>
                                </a>
                                <a class="dropdown-item d-flex py-3 border-bottom" href="#">
                                    <div class="me-3 notification-icon bg-danger d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
                                        <i class="fas fa-times-circle text-white"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
